{"id": "art-25136", "label": "Art. 25136", "title": "Art. 25136", "slug": "art-25136", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1590265852\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1555\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1590265852\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>36</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1409344069\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1554\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1409344069\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Fuziunea\ntransfrontalier&#259; realizat&#259; în conformitate cu <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span>\nart. 251<sup>23</sup> alin. (1) lit. a), c) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nd) are, de la data prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (3), urm&#259;toarele efecte:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_709834213\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1553\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_709834213\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)toate activele <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> pasivele\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> absorbite sunt transferate\nc&#259;tre societatea absorbant&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1859321223\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1552\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1859321223\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)<span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> absorbite devin <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span>\nai <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> absorbante, în conformitate\ncu regulile de repartizare stabilite în proiectul de fuziune, cu <span\nclass=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span> cazului în care <span class=SpellE>ace&#351;tia</span>\nau exercitat dreptul de retragere, potrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span>\nart. 251<sup>30</sup>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_539968958\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1551\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_539968958\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)societatea absorbit&#259; înceteaz&#259; s&#259; existe.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1188796354\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1550\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1188796354\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Fuziunea\ntransfrontalier&#259; realizat&#259; în conformitate cu art. 251<sup>23</sup>\nalin. (1) lit. b) are, de la data prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (3),\nurm&#259;toarele efecte:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1199501326\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1549\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1199501326\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)toate activele <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> pasivele\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> care fuzioneaz&#259; sunt\ntransferate c&#259;tre noua societate;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_736677115\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1548\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_736677115\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)<span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> care fuzioneaz&#259; devin <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> noii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>,\ncu <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span> cazului în care <span class=SpellE>ace&#351;tia</span>\nau exercitat dreptul de retragere, potrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span>\nart. 251<sup>30</sup>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_987214427\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1547\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_987214427\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Fuziunea produce\nefecte:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_3780771\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1546\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_3780771\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)în cazul constituirii unei <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>,\nde la data înmatricul&#259;rii acesteia în registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1034706679\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1545\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1034706679\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)în cazul fuziunii prin <span class=SpellE>absorb&#355;ie</span>,\nde la data înregistr&#259;rii în registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>\na actului modificator al actului constitutiv, cu <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span>\ncazului în care, prin acordul <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span>, se\nstipuleaz&#259; c&#259; <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunea</span> va avea\nefect la o alt&#259; dat&#259;, care nu poate fi îns&#259; ulterioar&#259;\nîncheierii <span class=SpellE>exerci&#355;iului</span> financiar curent al <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> absorbante <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nnici anterioar&#259; încheierii ultimului <span class=SpellE>exerci&#355;iu</span>\nfinanciar încheiat al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> sau <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> care <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span>\ntransfer&#259; activele <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> pasivele;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_226162893\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1544\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_226162893\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)în cazul în care prin fuziune se constituie o societate\neuropean&#259;, de la data înmatricul&#259;rii acesteia.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1400752506\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1543\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1400752506\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Drepturile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>obliga&#355;iile</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nabsorbite decurgând din contractele sau raporturile de munc&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> care exist&#259; la data intr&#259;rii în vigoare a\nfuziunii transfrontaliere se transfer&#259; de la data prev&#259;zut&#259; la\nalin. (3) <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> absorbante sau\nnou-constituite.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_30851388\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1542\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_30851388\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Niciuna dintre <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ile</span>\nsociale sau alte titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social al <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> absorbante nu poate fi schimbat&#259;\ncu <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;i</span>\nsociale sau alte titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social al <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> absorbite, <span class=SpellE>de&#355;inute</span>:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1666332169\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1541\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1666332169\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)fie de c&#259;tre societatea absorbant&#259; sau de\nc&#259;tre o persoan&#259; care <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ioneaz&#259;</span>\nîn nume propriu, dar pentru societatea respectiv&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_708094596\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1540\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_708094596\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)fie de c&#259;tre societatea absorbit&#259; sau de\nc&#259;tre o persoan&#259; care <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ioneaz&#259;</span>\nîn nume propriu, dar pentru societatea respectiv&#259;.</span></p>"}